queries.query: SELECT * FROM products;
SELECT productID, productName, unitPrice FROM products ORDER BY unitPrice DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_products FROM products;
SELECT categoryID, COUNT(*) AS product_count FROM products GROUP BY categoryID;
SELECT supplierID, COUNT(*) AS supplier_product_count FROM products GROUP BY supplierID;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE discontinued = '1';
SELECT productID, productName FROM products WHERE unitsInStock < reorderLevel;
SELECT categoryID, AVG(unitPrice) AS avg_price FROM products GROUP BY categoryID;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE unitPrice > 50 ORDER BY unitPrice DESC;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE unitsInStock > 100;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE productName LIKE 'C%';
SELECT * FROM products WHERE unitPrice BETWEEN 10 AND 20;
SELECT productID, productName FROM products WHERE unitsOnOrder > 0;
SELECT supplierID, SUM(unitsInStock) AS total_stock FROM products GROUP BY supplierID;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE categoryID = 1 ORDER BY unitPrice DESC;
SELECT productID, productName FROM products ORDER BY unitsInStock ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT categoryID, MIN(unitPrice) AS cheapest_product FROM products GROUP BY categoryID;
SELECT categoryID, MAX(unitPrice) AS most_expensive_product FROM products GROUP BY categoryID;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE unitsOnOrder > 50;
SELECT productID, productName FROM products WHERE reorderLevel > 20;
SELECT * FROM products WHERE supplierID = 3;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM products WHERE discontinued = '0';
